Problem Statement:2.2 
To implement an Android application using resource files to dynamically modify displayed text and background color through user interaction. 

STEP 1: Create the Android Project 
	Open Android Studio 
	Click → New Project 
	Choose Template 
	Select: 
	• Empty Views Activity 
	Click Next 
	Project Configuration (IMPORTANT) 
	Fill exactly like this (you may change app name slightly): 
	• Name: ResourceDemoApp 
	• Package name: auto-generated (leave it) 
	• Save location: default 
	• Language: Java 
	• Minimum SDK: API 21 or above 
	Click Finish 
	Wait till Gradle build completes. 

